steps.name: I launch the MVC site
I Add "Create Repo" Todo task
I should see "Create Repo" task available under "All" todo list
I should see "Create Repo" task available under "Active" todo list
I launch the MVC site

elements.name: Verify Number of Items left count matching with Active Tasks

steps.name: I Add "Active Task" Todo task
I Add "Active Task2" Todo task
I select "Active" filter
I should see number of items left count is matching with active tasks
I launch the MVC site
I Add "Completed Task" Todo task
I select "All" filter
I select "Completed Task" Todo task as completed
I should see "Completed Task" task marked as completed
I should see "Completed Task" task available under "Completed" todo list
I should see "Completed Task" task available under "All" todo list
I launch the MVC site

elements.name: Verify Number of Items left count

steps.name: I Add "Number of Items" Todo task
I should see number of items left displayed
I select "Number of Items" Todo task as completed
I should see number of items left count "decreased" by 1
I launch the MVC site
I launch the MVC site
I Add "Rename Task" Todo task
I select "All" filter
I rename "Rename Task" Todo task as "Updated Task"
I should see "Updated Task" task available under "All" todo list
I should see "Rename Task" task not available under "All" todo list
I launch the MVC site

elements.name: Verify Mark all tasks as completed

steps.name: I launch the MVC site
I Add "Mark All Task1" Todo task
I Add "Mark All Task2" Todo task
I select "All" filter
I mark all tasks as completed
I should see all tasks marked as completed
I should see 0 number of items left displayed
I launch the MVC site
I select "All" filter
I Add "Clear Completed Task" Todo task
I select "Clear Completed Task" Todo task as completed
I select "Completed" filter
I clear all completed tasks
I should see "Clear Completed Task" task not available under "All" todo list
I should see "Clear Completed Task" task not available under "Completed" todo list
